  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: First line is cut and not fully visible (only bottom half can be seen) If recipient name is long enough and takes 2 lines. Same happens if in total name and sum take 2 lines:\r\n1. Name is long (takes 2 lines)\r\n![screenshot_20170630-190928](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/27746540-4ea7c212-5dd0-11e7-9d4a-0b984f79e6a5.png)\r\n\r\n2. Sum and name are long (in total take 2 lines):\r\n![screenshot_20170630-190439](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/27746752-0d477104-5dd1-11e7-8a18-383ba031eee7.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAll lines (first 4 lines) in the input field are fully visible\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nFirst line is cut\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open group chat with a member who has long username, e.g. \"Anna Username with several words inside\"\r\n- tap on send command and select user name. Check the content of the input field after username is inserted\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version:  0.9.8-56-gd743691+\r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device Samsung Galaxy S7, Android 7.0\r\n",
